caption: #2016 #goodfood #healthy #healthyinspo #teresacutter  #thehealthychef  #purelydelicious  #healthychef

Jump on the nut butter boat! 
Our Macadamia Nut Butter is full of anti- inflammatory mono-unsaturated fats (like olive oil and avocado). To make, pour 3 cups of macadamia nuts into a blender and using the tamper press the macadamia nuts into the blades. Blend for less than a minute, until the creamy butter moves freely through the blades! If you add a few tablespoons of my Naked Chocolate and a little organic maple you can also make CHOCOLAT BUTTERğŸ’•ğŸ’— Store in the fridge for longer use.

HEALTHY CHEF BANANA ğŸŒ BREAD - This is my gluten free version from my latest Cookbook " The Healthy Chef PURELY DELICIOUS". Itâ€™s yummy on itâ€™s own or topped with a little ricotta + honey. 
GLUTEN FREE BANANA BREAD - BY TERESA CUTTER
300 g (10 Â½ oz) ripe banana,
smashed
3 free-range/organic eggs
60 g (2 fl oz) raw honey or organic
maple syrup
60 g (2 fl oz) extra virgin olive oil or macadamia nut oil
1 teaspoon vanilla extract
1 teaspoon ground cinnamon
Â½ teaspoon bicarbonate of soda (baking soda)
1 tablespoon lemon juice
280 g ( 9  3/4 oz) almond meal

PREHEAT your oven to 160Â°C (320Â°F).
COMBINE smashed banana, eggs, honey, oil, vanilla,
cinnamon, bicarbonate of soda and lemon juice (the lemon activates the bicarb).
ADD the almond meal and mix well.
LINE a loaf tin (10 1/2 cm wide and 26 cm long).
SPOON banana bread mixture into the tin.
BAKE for1 hour and enjoy.
